      "side": 1,
      "message": "Can you share a use case where offset + length extends beyond the 32bit range?\n\nDSP0267 v1.3.0 limits both fields to 32bits in the Component Image Information. Hence an overflow should ideally not exist. Even if it does, Update Agent should be able to check this and send Completion Code like Data Out of Range (0x82) or Invalid Transfer Length (0x83).\n\nSuggestion would be to limit the check to range of UNIT32.",
      "revId": "d5ab474d77d0bed1d17e3005d3e6cd12171dc462",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
    },
